{
  "id": "2023-03-16_screen_english",
  "date": "2023-03-16",
  "corner": "screen_english",
  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "I suppose we can cope with feeding one",
  "movie": "",
  "duration_sec": 782.59,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2023-03-16_screen_english.mp3",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 22.08,
      "text": "English, 배달 서비스, 스크린 잉글리시 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.08,
      "end": 24.06,
      "text": "3월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.06,
      "end": 28.84,
      "text": "Based on Colin Tilly's 1964 Children's Book"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.84,
      "end": 30.3,
      "text": "Storm Boy"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.3,
      "end": 33.66,
      "text": "이제 정말 익숙해진 이름입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 33.88,
      "end": 38.8,
      "text": "Colin Tilly's의 Children's Book의 기본으로 만들어진 영화죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 38.86,
      "end": 40.2,
      "text": "Practice makes perfect."
    },
    {
      "start": 40.96,
      "end": 42.2,
      "text": "Thanks to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 42.48,
      "end": 43.64,
      "text": "Thanks to your help."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.12,
      "end": 44.7,
      "text": "Thanks to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.92,
      "end": 46.4,
      "text": "Thanks to me."
    },
    {
      "start": 46.52,
      "end": 46.8,
      "text": "You're right."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.18,
      "end": 47.44,
      "text": "Tilly."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.92,
      "end": 48.76,
      "text": "Thanks to Masubang."
    },
    {
      "start": 48.84,
      "end": 50.26,
      "text": "제가 혼나가지고."
    },
    {
      "start": 50.5,
      "end": 50.92,
      "text": "그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 50.92,
      "end": 54.36,
      "text": "우리 Storm Boy 이야기를 이어가고 있는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.36,
      "end": 58.2,
      "text": "펠리콘 새 친구들 벌써부터 너무 보고 싶어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 58.54,
      "end": 59.28,
      "text": "아, 벌써요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.38,
      "end": 59.58,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 59.78,
      "end": 62.08,
      "text": "그 마이클이 자연으로 떠나보냈잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 62.42,
      "end": 64.36,
      "text": "과연 잘 살고 있으려나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.0,
      "end": 70.36,
      "text": "Well, it is hard to live in the wild if you've grown up, pampered your whole life."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.52,
      "end": 72.86,
      "text": "They've been fed, bathed."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.26,
      "end": 74.84,
      "text": "And Michael did everything for them."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.92,
      "end": 75.3,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.88,
      "end": 77.74,
      "text": "어렸을 때 막 추어탕도 해먹이고."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.74,
      "end": 78.3,
      "text": "그러니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.5,
      "end": 80.14,
      "text": "그 맛있는 추어탕이."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.92,
      "end": 85.16,
      "text": "그나저나, I wonder if they have their own names."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.88,
      "end": 90.64,
      "text": "Mr. Proud하고, Mr. Ponder하고, Mr. Percival."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.02,
      "end": 94.88,
      "text": "이게 진짜 걔네들의 이름인지, 아니면 실제 이름이 또 있는지."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.0,
      "end": 95.96,
      "text": "아, real life names."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.28,
      "end": 97.16,
      "text": "Real life bird names."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.62,
      "end": 98.62,
      "text": "In fact, they did."
    },
    {
      "start": 98.7,
      "end": 99.26,
      "text": "진짜요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.26,
      "end": 104.64,
      "text": "Yes, according to my research, the actor pelicans had actual real names."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.28,
      "end": 105.84,
      "text": "Dumb-dumb."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.18,
      "end": 106.74,
      "text": "Dumb-dumb."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.8,
      "end": 108.82,
      "text": "Not like 바보�dumb, but D-U-M."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.16,
      "end": 109.92,
      "text": "Dumb-dumb."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.12,
      "end": 110.98,
      "text": "Kind of cute."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.12,
      "end": 111.7,
      "text": "너무 귀엽네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.94,
      "end": 112.5,
      "text": "Carpenter."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.5,
      "end": 114.1,
      "text": "Carpenter."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.42,
      "end": 115.82,
      "text": "You know, a carpenter."
    },
    {
      "start": 116.62,
      "end": 117.02,
      "text": "목수."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.02,
      "end": 117.44,
      "text": "목수."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.44,
      "end": 119.26,
      "text": "That's kind of interesting."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.62,
      "end": 121.36,
      "text": "왜 목수라는 이름을 지었을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.68,
      "end": 123.4,
      "text": "나무를 뭔가 되게 좋아했나?"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.62,
      "end": 124.22,
      "text": "그런 거요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.34,
      "end": 127.8,
      "text": "Like, well, did he hit a tree with his beak?"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.34,
      "end": 129.28,
      "text": "Like a woodpecker?"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.58,
      "end": 130.12,
      "text": "Peck, peck, peck."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.12,
      "end": 131.32,
      "text": "And sandwich."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.84,
      "end": 134.08,
      "text": "아니, sandwich는, 아, 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 134.22,
      "end": 138.96,
      "text": "Dumb-dumb이랑 Carpenter는 그렇다고 치고, 이 sandwich는 과연, what was he good at?"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.22,
      "end": 143.04,
      "text": "Pelicans say, people are having picnics on the beach, having sandwiches."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.42,
      "end": 147.54,
      "text": "They swoop down and they steal the people's sandwiches while they're in the water."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.54,
      "end": 149.5,
      "text": "The people are going for a swim."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.0,
      "end": 150.76,
      "text": "그렇지 않았을까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.98,
      "end": 153.0,
      "text": "굉장히 설득적인 추론이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.04,
      "end": 153.84,
      "text": "한번 추측해 봅니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.84,
      "end": 161.66,
      "text": "저는 막 거기에 모래가 많으니까, 막 모래에 막 파묻고 그래가지고 샌드에서 뭔가 따와서 샌드위치라고 지었나?"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.1,
      "end": 162.82,
      "text": "이랬는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 162.9,
      "end": 163.78,
      "text": "아, 모래 샌드."
    },
    {
      "start": 164.46,
      "end": 167.24,
      "text": "그런데 큿샘이 더 맞는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 167.44,
      "end": 168.36,
      "text": "우리의 추측이지만."
    },
    {
      "start": 168.5,
      "end": 170.48,
      "text": "아, 이게 뭐, 노답이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 170.82,
      "end": 171.94,
      "text": "정답은 없습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 172.16,
      "end": 172.32,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 173.04,
      "end": 176.26,
      "text": "정답은 모르겠으나 우리의 추측이 맞을 거라고 믿어봅니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 176.48,
      "end": 177.16,
      "text": "Sandwich."
    },
    {
      "start": 177.32,
      "end": 178.6,
      "text": "Anyway, cute names."
    },
    {
      "start": 179.22,
      "end": 182.12,
      "text": "And it took 12 months to train these cute little pelicans."
    },
    {
      "start": 182.12,
      "end": 183.08,
      "text": "12 months."
    },
    {
      "start": 183.1,
      "end": 183.6,
      "text": "A whole year."
    },
    {
      "start": 183.84,
      "end": 188.72,
      "text": "And according to the trainer, 덤덤, was the most adventurous pelican."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.98,
      "end": 191.56,
      "text": "He liked to wander off and escape."
    },
    {
      "start": 192.34,
      "end": 193.28,
      "text": "He didn't want to work."
    },
    {
      "start": 194.54,
      "end": 195.72,
      "text": "He just 도망가고 싶었죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.84,
      "end": 200.1,
      "text": "그래서 너무 귀여워서 장난꾸러기라서 덤덤이라고 지었나 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 200.22,
      "end": 200.66,
      "text": "덤덤."
    },
    {
      "start": 200.74,
      "end": 201.22,
      "text": "덤덤."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.24,
      "end": 202.34,
      "text": "덤덤 ran away again."
    },
    {
      "start": 202.72,
      "end": 203.56,
      "text": "Come back, 덤덤."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.0,
      "end": 204.16,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.84,
      "end": 208.74,
      "text": "아무튼 실제 이름을 들어보니까 더욱 더 친숙해지는 느낌이 듭니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.0,
      "end": 209.38,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.38,
      "end": 217.14,
      "text": "There was also apparently a famous dance, a dance scene on the beach where storm boy is dancing with the pelican."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.14,
      "end": 217.62,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.62,
      "end": 220.42,
      "text": "So the bird and the boy are dancing on the beach."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.42,
      "end": 220.5,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.5,
      "end": 222.18,
      "text": "And how is this possible?"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.5,
      "end": 225.88,
      "text": "Apparently, it was not scripted."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.88,
      "end": 229.6,
      "text": "It was all ad lib, improvised dance."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.72,
      "end": 230.76,
      "text": "와우, ad lib이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.76,
      "end": 232.72,
      "text": "그냥 즉석으로 ad lib."
    },
    {
      "start": 232.72,
      "end": 240.48,
      "text": "그러니까 서로 교감이 많이 되어 있는 상태이다 보니까 이게 자연스럽게 나오게 된 장면이었군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 240.72,
      "end": 243.7,
      "text": "And good timing because the camera was right there."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.78,
      "end": 244.18,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 244.28,
      "end": 246.34,
      "text": "And they shot this ad lib dance."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.42,
      "end": 246.78,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.9,
      "end": 248.48,
      "text": "And it made for a memorable scene."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.6,
      "end": 249.56,
      "text": "Beautiful scene."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.68,
      "end": 250.02,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.44,
      "end": 252.48,
      "text": "이 장면도 굉장히 인상 깊었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.34,
      "end": 255.12,
      "text": "자, 오늘 준비된 내용 듣고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.12,
      "end": 257.03,
      "text": "It's Mr. Percival!"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.53,
      "end": 258.27,
      "text": "He came back!"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.52,
      "end": 260.12,
      "text": "Stay, Carnie!"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.97,
      "end": 263.01,
      "text": "Yeah, I suppose we can cope with feeding one."
    },
    {
      "start": 264.0,
      "end": 267.86,
      "text": "From that day on, Mr. Percival refused to ever leave my side."
    },
    {
      "start": 268.42,
      "end": 269.2,
      "text": "Not for an hour."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.9,
      "end": 271.02,
      "text": "Not for a minute."
    },
    {
      "start": 271.74,
      "end": 272.06,
      "text": "Never."
    },
    {
      "start": 272.94,
      "end": 273.3,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.66,
      "end": 274.82,
      "text": "You stay here and I'll hide."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.22,
      "end": 275.8,
      "text": "No peeking."
    },
    {
      "start": 276.3,
      "end": 277.76,
      "text": "Make sure he doesn't cheat."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.2,
      "end": 279.52,
      "text": "And count to ten for him."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.52,
      "end": 287.8,
      "text": "One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten."
    },
    {
      "start": 288.22,
      "end": 289.94,
      "text": "All right, Mr. Percival, go find him."
    },
    {
      "start": 290.26,
      "end": 290.74,
      "text": "Come on."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.3,
      "end": 292.42,
      "text": "You told him then."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.5,
      "end": 293.32,
      "text": "She told him."
    },
    {
      "start": 294.44,
      "end": 295.7,
      "text": "I know it."
    },
    {
      "start": 295.9,
      "end": 301.36,
      "text": "저는 특히 다른 애들은 몰라도 Percival는 꼭 올 거라고 예상을 했었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.72,
      "end": 303.18,
      "text": "Because they're best."
    },
    {
      "start": 304.3,
      "end": 304.98,
      "text": "BFFs."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.04,
      "end": 305.34,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.34,
      "end": 309.5,
      "text": "He was sitting on the roof of an outdoor toilet."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.74,
      "end": 311.4,
      "text": "Was it a toilet?"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.56,
      "end": 311.84,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.96,
      "end": 313.02,
      "text": "Oh, an outhouse."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.08,
      "end": 313.44,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.64,
      "end": 314.82,
      "text": "Outhouse가 있었잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 315.14,
      "end": 316.76,
      "text": "With the, it's a wooden toilet."
    },
    {
      "start": 316.9,
      "end": 317.16,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 317.3,
      "end": 319.96,
      "text": "You have to clean out the, you know, excrement."
    },
    {
      "start": 320.36,
      "end": 320.8,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 320.92,
      "end": 322.96,
      "text": "그건 옛날에 해본 적 있죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.16,
      "end": 326.38,
      "text": "근데 그 지붕에 왜 걔가, 냄새가 안 났나?"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.5,
      "end": 327.6,
      "text": "왜 거기 올라갔을까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 328.16,
      "end": 328.6,
      "text": "What's it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 328.64,
      "end": 329.18,
      "text": "A bird?"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.54,
      "end": 329.76,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 329.82,
      "end": 330.74,
      "text": "Natural smell."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.94,
      "end": 333.78,
      "text": "And the boy was inside the toilet."
    },
    {
      "start": 333.78,
      "end": 334.8,
      "text": "Oh, he was."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.8,
      "end": 334.98,
      "text": "아니요."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.98,
      "end": 342.54,
      "text": "아침에 눈을 뜨고 이제 토일렛을 가려고 가다가 지붕을 딱 보고, 와, Percival 이렇게 된 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 342.84,
      "end": 345.6,
      "text": "그럼 그 주인 냄새 맡았나 봐."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.74,
      "end": 347.02,
      "text": "Oh, that's him."
    },
    {
      "start": 348.64,
      "end": 351.14,
      "text": "아, 정말 창의적인 추론이셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 351.14,
      "end": 356.86,
      "text": "아, 정말 기분이 좋아지는 장면이었고, 심지어 they played hide-and-seek together."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.28,
      "end": 357.64,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.76,
      "end": 358.14,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 358.22,
      "end": 359.92,
      "text": "Percival's pretty good at hide-and-seek."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.0,
      "end": 360.22,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.6,
      "end": 365.32,
      "text": "펠리컨하고 이렇게 숨바꼭질이 가능하다는 것을 이 영화를 통해서 처음 봤어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 365.78,
      "end": 366.44,
      "text": "That's, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 366.5,
      "end": 368.56,
