      "text": "Yeah, very nice."
    },
    {
      "start": 705.4,
      "end": 705.84,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 706.16,
      "end": 711.02,
      "text": "이렇게 pelican으로 인해서 가족이 훨씬 더 끈끈해지는 장면이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 711.8,
      "end": 713.26,
      "text": "자, 다시 한번 확인해보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 713.9,
      "end": 714.94,
      "text": "It's Mr. Percival."
    },
    {
      "start": 715.48,
      "end": 716.22,
      "text": "He came back."
    },
    {
      "start": 717.08,
      "end": 718.06,
      "text": "He can stay, can't he?"
    },
    {
      "start": 718.89,
      "end": 720.93,
      "text": "Yeah, I suppose we can cope with feeding one."
    },
    {
      "start": 721.96,
      "end": 725.78,
      "text": "From that day on, Mr. Percival refused to ever leave my side."
    },
    {
      "start": 726.34,
      "end": 727.12,
      "text": "Not for an hour."
    },
    {
      "start": 727.84,
      "end": 728.94,
      "text": "Not for a minute."
    },
    {
      "start": 729.7,
      "end": 729.98,
      "text": "Never."
    },
    {
      "start": 730.89,
      "end": 731.21,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 731.59,
      "end": 732.75,
      "text": "You stay here and I'll hide."
    },
    {
      "start": 733.15,
      "end": 733.71,
      "text": "No peeking."
    },
    {
      "start": 734.27,
      "end": 735.69,
      "text": "Make sure he doesn't cheat."
    },
    {
      "start": 735.69,
      "end": 737.45,
      "text": "And count to 10 for him."
    },
    {
      "start": 737.97,
      "end": 745.71,
      "text": "One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.13,
      "end": 747.87,
      "text": "All right, Mr. Percival, go find him."
    },
    {
      "start": 748.19,
      "end": 748.63,
      "text": "Come on."
    },
    {
      "start": 749.23,
      "end": 750.33,
      "text": "You told him, Dad."
    },
    {
      "start": 750.39,
      "end": 751.23,
      "text": "She told him."
    },
    {
      "start": 752.25,
      "end": 754.67,
      "text": "네, 아주 행복한 장면이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 755.17,
      "end": 757.57,
      "text": "근데 이게 계속 이어지면 얼마나 좋을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.09,
      "end": 759.39,
      "text": "Yeah, forever."
    },
    {
      "start": 759.79,
      "end": 760.13,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 760.13,
      "end": 763.93,
      "text": "근데 왠지 그러지 않을 것 같은 예감이 살짝 들긴 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 764.17,
      "end": 765.45,
      "text": "Another twist is coming."
    },
    {
      "start": 765.45,
      "end": 771.49,
      "text": "차상희님께서 Very Cute Teacher, 크쌤이라고 보내주셨네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 771.77,
      "end": 772.87,
      "text": "Oh, very cute."
    },
    {
      "start": 772.99,
      "end": 774.01,
      "text": "I like that."
    },
    {
      "start": 774.13,
      "end": 774.99,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 775.55,
      "end": 779.27,
      "text": "네, 오늘도 이렇게 즐겁게 함께해 주셔서 너무너무 감사드립니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 779.51,
      "end": 780.45,
      "text": "I had fun too."
    },
    {
      "start": 780.49,
      "end": 781.45,
      "text": "Yeah, thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 781.87,
      "end": 782.59,
      "text": "See you next Monday."
    }
  ]
}